{"tid":746124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民族黨單嘢 湯家驊為保安局辯護 又被秒殺","createTime":"2018-07-17T10:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T05:18:02.000Z","uid":138409,"like":320,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"1d23e15a2ded2856a6477db04238d80ea7d1cade","tid":746124,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:18:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2190224034340590&amp;id=211789612184052\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2190224034340590%26id%3D211789612184052&d=cdjQsK2mD6yhG1gQ%2Fe%2Fj%2BZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=6346f07e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2190224034340590&amp;id=211789612184052</a><br />\n<br />\nEdward Wong:<br />\n<br />\n簡直不知所謂<br />\n<br />\n在X v Italy, App No 6741/74 (European Commission on Human Rights, Plenary, 21 May 1976)一案中，歐洲人權委員會（而非歐洲人權法庭）指禁止法西斯主義者組黨並無構成歧視，因其追求的目的 - 即保護民主體制 - 為合法目的。委員會從無如你所指拒絕任何主張推翻現行政治體制的人的結社自由，更無直接將推翻現行政治體制等同「危及在這政冶體制下之人民享有之權利和自由」。<br />\n<br />\n自1976年後，X v Italy從未獲歐洲人權法院或歐洲人權委員會確認或引用。無論如何，不論X v Italy作為案例的法律效力為何，歐洲人權法院早於2000年Sadak and Others v Turkey, App No 25144/94, 26149/95, 26150/95, 26151/95, 26152/95, 26154/95, 27100/95, 27101/95 &amp; 26153/95 (ECtHR, 30 May 2000)一案中，認為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">單憑X v Italy，不能直接構成解散分離主義政黨的法律依據。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n湯家驊資深大律師，你可否停止（我希望不是故意地）扭曲國際人權法（尤其是《歐洲人權公約》）？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/181614_72ffc2577ca39b76fd3cefb190526026.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F181614_72ffc2577ca39b76fd3cefb190526026.jpg&h=fa4b0ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/181613_78347ed777a2cd0ab68c9ad58c69e4ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F181613_78347ed777a2cd0ab68c9ad58c69e4ca.jpg&h=f44ab19d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d1a0cec6632cf1fa378163a3353a0bf9c3837f3","tid":746124,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:21:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b02cfdec2d24a4757fc49505b101b14fc8cc28c8","tid":746124,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:22:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ed65a7650b1e4f0e467b31eabb643e0db9b886f9","tid":746124,"uid":34927,"like":1,"dislike":48,"score":-47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:24:33.000Z","msg":"like．reply．1m<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4864e462b16dec9f948981b5f4c94e83a95680be","tid":746124,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:29:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f562ad91607be1095b15ae23d42421c7e172b24a","tid":746124,"uid":4783,"like":136,"dislike":0,"score":136,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"又係比卡超大狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次十一哥都俾佢秒殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa750974b955de718eb58dfdee6898aa27838c8","tid":746124,"uid":2471,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:31:46.000Z","msg":"比卡超又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c92f772801e7c5dd9f902546840086e6e20070","tid":746124,"uid":138409,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"quote":{"pid":"f562ad91607be1095b15ae23d42421c7e172b24a","tid":746124,"uid":4783,"like":136,"dislike":0,"score":136,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"又係比卡超大狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次十一哥都俾佢秒殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:34:00.000Z","msg":"香港需要更多比卡超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲妖言惑眾嘅狀棍實在害人不淺"},{"pid":"3e60d1c5bd1b48c65881d26b69c4022e1a87ebcf","tid":746124,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d312fdcb4af319a1f848bc0edc8b0ee24dfa664d","tid":746124,"uid":36901,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:34:25.000Z","msg":"禁止法西斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係都中共&amp;愛字頭先啦"},{"pid":"0f55ce6d40149dacc862bebc5b01c60bb806cc04","tid":746124,"uid":138409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3aa750974b955de718eb58dfdee6898aa27838c8","tid":746124,"uid":2471,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:31:46.000Z","msg":"比卡超又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:34:27.000Z","msg":"有11哥嘅地方就有比卡超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba820198ede9f572b594a0b567280a9e3a806f81","tid":746124,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c2d9e85106922ca5a19d62fb4af92a5f13a4ef","tid":746124,"uid":5499,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:35:40.000Z","msg":"瘋狂追殺11哥"},{"pid":"b2dc1e357d628dc9738ee3d28b90254bb73810dd","tid":746124,"uid":138409,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"d312fdcb4af319a1f848bc0edc8b0ee24dfa664d","tid":746124,"uid":36901,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:34:25.000Z","msg":"禁止法西斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係都中共&amp;愛字頭先啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:36:17.000Z","msg":"法西斯個case係響意大利嘅<br />\n咁湯家驊用呢個case合理化警方建議啊嘛<br />\n咁咪用返呢個case駁佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中共&amp;愛字頭暫時應該咪spread去意大利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0621609ac5dc2b3e106ded8e23e03256de0ad4","tid":746124,"uid":96,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:36:19.000Z","msg":"所以衰十一也是社團活動<br />\n<br />\n個留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa08428fcd1e3a2ca808569ff5b76d515b12ad15","tid":746124,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e0621609ac5dc2b3e106ded8e23e03256de0ad4","tid":746124,"uid":96,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:36:19.000Z","msg":"所以衰十一也是社團活動<br />\n<br />\n個留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"多於一人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e082bd42cebed60e27788da162bd8692029590e","tid":746124,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:40:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6faccf545f7b4759125a5049b35a48436bbce195","tid":746124,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:45:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eb367e41f9e8b480c577734b67255aa07871e842","tid":746124,"uid":138409,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:49:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/184854_aa308b55ac17548da30bb6bf6f34cc5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F184854_aa308b55ac17548da30bb6bf6f34cc5b.png&h=99a56eea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nEdward Wong:<br />\n歐洲人權法院歷年來不只一次裁定，尋求獨立的分離主義政黨，即使其主張和現行的政治體制原則有所衝突，但只要沒有直接鼓吹暴力，獨立主張本身沒有違反民主原則，政府因此而懲罰分離主義政黨（尤其是採取解散政黨此最嚴重的手段），是嚴重侵犯結社自由。"},{"pid":"f4d43da55f89e975111f35c089e063bd08d06521","tid":746124,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb367e41f9e8b480c577734b67255aa07871e842","tid":746124,"uid":138409,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:49:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/184854_aa308b55ac17548da30bb6bf6f34cc5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F184854_aa308b55ac17548da30bb6bf6f34cc5b.png&h=99a56eea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nEdward Wong:<br />\n歐洲人權法院歷年來不只一次裁定，尋求獨立的分離主義政黨，即使其主張和現行的政治體制原則有所衝突，但只要沒有直接鼓吹暴力，獨立主張本身沒有違反民主原則，政府因此而懲罰分離主義政黨（尤其是採取解散政黨此最嚴重的手段），是嚴重侵犯結社自由。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:49:29.000Z","msg":"'56. ... [T]he interference at issue in the present case was radical: the applicant party was dissolved with immediate effect. Such a drastic measure requires very serious reasons by way of justification before it could be considered proportionate to the legitimate aim pursued; it would be warranted only in the most serious cases.<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n59 The Court considers that it was not unreasonable for the authorities to suspect that certain leaders or members of the applicant party harboured separatist views and had a political agenda that included the notion of autonomy for the region of Pirin Macedonia or even its secession from Bulgaria. However, it reiterates that a political party may campaign for a change in the legal and constitutional structures of the state on two conditions: first, the means used to that end must in every respect be legal and democratic, and secondly, the change proposed must itself be compatible with fundamental democratic principles. There is no indication that these conditions were not present in the case at hand.<br />\n<br />\n60 As regards the first condition, it is noteworthy that on none of the occasions cited by the Constitutional Court in its judgment the applicant party's leaders and members hinted at any intention to use violence or any other undemocratic means to achieve their aims. There is, furthermore, no indication in the case file that any practical actions were undertaken by the applicant party which could pose a threat to Bulgaria's national security. In this connection, the Court observes that the incidents referred to by the Constitutional Court were rallies, speeches, press conferences, letters or maps, in which members of the applicant party or of its predecessor organisations had stated that there existed a Macedonian minority in Bulgaria and that the Pirin region was not part of Bulgaria, and had made certain peaceful demands in that respect."},{"pid":"b03fe67f4d6da56ef74dfac649ae23791d459ae5","tid":746124,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:49:40.000Z","msg":"61 Concerning the second condition, the Court considers that even if it may be assumed that the political project advocated by the applicant party was indeed the autonomy or even secession of Pirin Macedonia, this does not automatically mean that it was at variance with the principles of democracy. ...<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;the fact that a group of persons calls for autonomy or even requests secession of part of the country's territory &mdash; thus demanding fundamental constitutional and territorial changes &mdash; cannot automatically justify a prohibition of its assemblies&rdquo;.<br />\n<br />\n... The mere fact that a political party calls for autonomy or even requests secession of part of the country's territory is not a sufficient basis to justify its dissolution on national security grounds. In a democratic society based on the rule of law, political ideas which challenge the existing order without putting into question the tenets of democracy, and whose realisation is advocated by peaceful means must be afforded a proper opportunity of expression through, inter alia, participation in the political process. However shocking and unacceptable the statements of the applicant party's leaders and members may appear to the authorities or the majority of the population and however illegitimate their demands may be, they do not appear to warrant the impugned interference. The fact that the applicant party's political programme was considered incompatible with the current principles and structures of the Bulgarian State does not make it incompatible with the rules and principles of democracy. It is of the essence of democracy to allow diverse political programmes to be proposed and debated, even those that call into question the way a state is currently organised, provided that they do not harm democracy itself. ...<br />\n<br />\n62. In sum, the Court considers that there did not exist a pressing social need to order the applicant party&rsquo;s dissolution and that the dissolution was thus not necessary in a democratic society, within the meaning of Article 11 of the Convention.'<br />\n<br />\n- United Macedonian Organisation Ilinden-Pirin v Bulgaria (2006) 43 EHRR 52"},{"pid":"d769553b35e5764afaa11b957bf66f0ff2a21509","tid":746124,"uid":128261,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:52:34.000Z","msg":"呢單野打上法庭政府好大機會輸，除非支那釋法<br />\n根據普通法呢個人係徹底違反結社自由"},{"pid":"d56bc08f17213834bae0cb8ae3630fa95ade246e","tid":746124,"uid":138409,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"d769553b35e5764afaa11b957bf66f0ff2a21509","tid":746124,"uid":1282