score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:18:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2190224034340590&amp;id=211789612184052\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2190224034340590%26id%3D211789612184052&d=cdjQsK2mD6yhG1gQ%2Fe%2Fj%2BZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=6346f07e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2190224034340590&amp;id=211789612184052</a><br />\n<br />\nEdward Wong:<br />\n<br />\n簡直不知所謂<br />\n<br />\n在X v Italy, App No 6741/74 (European Commission on Human Rights, Plenary, 21 May 1976)一案中，歐洲人權委員會（而非歐洲人權法庭）指禁止法西斯主義者組黨並無構成歧視，因其追求的目的 - 即保護民主體制 - 為合法目的。委員會從無如你所指拒絕任何主張推翻現行政治體制的人的結社自由，更無直接將推翻現行政治體制等同「危及在這政冶體制下之人民享有之權利和自由」。<br />\n<br />\n自1976年後，X v Italy從未獲歐洲人權法院或歐洲人權委員會確認或引用。無論如何，不論X v Italy作為案例的法律效力為何，歐洲人權法院早於2000年Sadak and Others v Turkey, App No 25144/94, 26149/95, 26150/95, 26151/95, 26152/95, 26154/95, 27100/95, 27101/95 &amp; 26153/95 (ECtHR, 30 May 2000)一案中，認為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">單憑X v Italy，不能直接構成解散分離主義政黨的法律依據。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n湯家驊資深大律師，你可否停止（我希望不是故意地）扭曲國際人權法（尤其是《歐洲人權公約》）？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/181614_72ffc2577ca39b76fd3cefb190526026.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F181614_72ffc2577ca39b76fd3cefb190526026.jpg&h=fa4b0ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/181613_78347ed777a2cd0ab68c9ad58c69e4ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F181613_78347ed777a2cd0ab68c9ad58c69e4ca.jpg&h=f44ab19d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:07:18.000Z","msg":"提倡推翻一國兩制既黨派要取締<br />\n<br />\n共黨直頭用行動去推翻一國兩制，實行一國一制，咁特首係咪又可以取締共黨🤔"},{"pid":"15d8a376cdaaddc741461bd93929ce7b6db1562a","tid":746124,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:08:27.000Z","msg":"雪廠街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c2ac6df6ed077b5c7d6484d911c6aef0f4e416","tid":746124,"uid":128261,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"90b5ac722a90c1c5ce1ec117993b5057ce8ddce1","tid":746124,"uid":68896,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1d23e15a2ded2856a6477db04238d80ea7d1cade","tid":746124,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:18:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2190224034340590&amp;id=211789612184052\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2190224034340590%26id%3D211789612184052&d=cdjQsK2mD6yhG1gQ%2Fe%2Fj%2BZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=6346f07e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2190224034340590&amp;id=211789612184052</a><br />\n<br />\nEdward Wong:<br />\n<br />\n簡直不知所謂<br />\n<br />\n在X v Italy, App No 6741/74 (European Commission on Human Rights, Plenary, 21 May 1976)一案中，歐洲人權委員會（而非歐洲人權法庭）指禁止法西斯主義者組黨並無構成歧視，因其追求的目的 - 即保護民主體制 - 為合法目的。委員會從無如你所指拒絕任何主張推翻現行政治體制的人的結社自由，更無直接將推翻現行政治體制等同「危及在這政冶體制下之人民享有之權利和自由」。<br />\n<br />\n自1976年後，X v Italy從未獲歐洲人權法院或歐洲人權委員會確認或引用。無論如何，不論X v Italy作為案例的法律效力為何，歐洲人權法院早於2000年Sadak and Others v Turkey, App No 25144/94, 26149/95, 26150/95, 26151/95, 26152/95, 26154/95, 27100/95, 27101/95 &amp; 26153/95 (ECtHR, 30 May 2000)一案中，認為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">單憑X v Italy，不能直接構成解散分離主義政黨的法律依據。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n湯家驊資深大律師，你可否停止（我希望不是故意地）扭曲國際人權法（尤其是《歐洲人權公約》）？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/181614_72ffc2577ca39b76fd3cefb190526026.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F181614_72ffc2577ca39b76fd3cefb190526026.jpg&h=fa4b0ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/181613_78347ed777a2cd0ab68c9ad58c69e4ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F181613_78347ed777a2cd0ab68c9ad58c69e4ca.jpg&h=f44ab19d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:07:18.000Z","msg":"提倡推翻一國兩制既黨派要取締<br />\n<br />\n共黨直頭用行動去推翻一國兩制，實行一國一制，咁特首係咪又可以取締共黨🤔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:09:18.000Z","msg":"你咁講係無意義，因為一國兩制解釋權係共產黨自己度<br />\n重點係唔可以再比共產黨用一國兩制呢塊假面具黎呃人"},{"pid":"3d766719ce9540eccc54f27464c87e9aeb9c13ed","tid":746124,"uid":170383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0011662058d343da207cf82b331dddf816e2688","tid":746124,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3c6393b94d9981d8a3a27ad6e6e3458bad1ae11","tid":746124,"uid":128261,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"f75d46edf748cf665640d12825fa71dcf511fda6","tid":746124,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c7763934ca4fc04f36952fb0bbbd60353ff6c00","tid":746124,"uid":128261,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:57:40.000Z","msg":"起碼證明鬼佬既普通法框架之下已經提供足夠保障比公民<br />\n係你地班支那小農搞釋法破壞<br />\n支那同西方既分野就更加明顯<br />\n香港既西洋鏡就會徹底被拆穿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:59:20.000Z","msg":"佢敢釋法就真係好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:06:46.000Z","msg":"我好撚憎港共仲keep佢「法治」既西洋鏡呃神騙鬼<br />\n拆穿佢攬炒好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:16:12.000Z","msg":