gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:59:04.000Z","msg":"其實如果用呢個案例黎做，工聯會係最大機會俾人用社團條例勒令解散既政黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7372fec96a30e669ba31ad70b065d10dffa8d68","tid":746124,"uid":192263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T12:22:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9811adb69be1e7e81eb00fb654133b894e2ae625","tid":746124,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95c1afac51a85555b09d2bfe18a3a5e297e21136","tid":746124,"uid":128261,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6a0cfcda3b6a73bed320393416e81ac1de1758c5","tid":746124,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:22:55.000Z","msg":"我理解出黎，係咪即係話共產黨視民族黨為法西斯政黨？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:29:01.000Z","msg":"主張分離以達到自由既分離主義，同主張消滅民主自由制度既法西斯主義，根本無可比性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T12:23:58.000Z","msg":"可比性就一定無<br />\n重點唔係佢地係咪法西斯<br />\n而係共產黨宣布某人係法西斯主義者<br />\n<br />\n如果共產黨宣布他人係法西斯主義者，宣布香港獨派係法西斯組織<br />\n咁差唔多可以肯定<br />\n香港必然獨立"},{"pid":"ec064c519331819d8b75f1c5b927e10a6a05b8af","tid":746124,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T12:31:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>淚</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b3153b116782bf8282c53082c817783085535812","tid":746124,"uid":30633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T12:32:57.000Z","msg":"比卡超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173e57df1ee6a3fc6655e2696cb7f8a359e46a46","tid":746124,"uid":114524,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T12:52:21.000Z","msg":"比卡超正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再新少少嘅案例HADEP v Turkey (2013) 56 EHRR 5，歐洲人權法庭直頭開到口話對「保持領土完整」係咪可以作為解散政黨嘅合法目的(legitimate aim)有保留。<br />\n<br />\n[44] The Court observes that the Constitutional Court decided to dissolve HADEP because it was deemed to be centre of illegal activities against the indivisible unity of the state within its nation. Contrary to what was submitted by the Government, however, the Court has hesitations as to whether the dissolution of a political party in order to maintain the indivisible unity of the state with its nation can be said to have pursued the legitimate aims of preventing disorder, protecting the rights of others and protecting territorial integrity and thus preserving national security."},{"pid":"78d90f2f86a4bcd6162013d5fd60607108a6a33d","tid":746124,"uid":86726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T12:53:27.000Z","msg":"推爆湯渣條撚樣"},{"pid":"da911179883d3128889cfff010d44276249e4009","tid":746124,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f149a566e0113ce5e41a1dc309d7547340ea0a","tid":746124,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95c1afac51a85555b09d2bfe18a3a5e297e21136","tid":746124,"uid":128261,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6a0cfcda3b6a73bed320393416e81ac1de1758c5","tid":746124,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:22:55.000Z","msg":"我理解出黎，係咪即係話共產黨視民族黨為法西斯政黨？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:29:01.000Z","msg":"主張分離以達到自由既分離主義，同主張消滅民主自由制度既法西斯主義，根本無可比性"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:30:58.000Z","msg":"簡而精"},{"pid":"5859b205d7040d326c0bc71dc60d9ea74d0405d7","tid":746124,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"173e57df1ee6a3fc6655e2696cb7f8a359e46a46","tid":746124,"uid":114524,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T12:52:21.000Z","msg":"比卡超正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再新少少嘅案例HADEP v Turkey (2013) 56 EHRR 5，歐洲人權法庭直頭開到口話對「保持領土完整」係咪可以作為解散政黨嘅合法目的(legitimate aim)有保留。<br />\n<br />\n[44] The Court observes that the Constitutional Court decided to dissolve HADEP because it was deemed to be centre of illegal activities against the indivisible unity of the state within its nation. Contrary to what was submitted by the Government, however, the Court has hesitations as to whether the dissolution of a political party in order to maintain the indivisible unity of the state with its nation can be said to have pursued the legitimate aims of preventing disorder, protecting the rights of others and protecting territorial integrity and thus preserving national security."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671c6a65b3896ff9a06eec09971b7446bebda7f7","tid":746124,"uid":145625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T13:35:52.000Z","msg":"[img]<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/17/213454_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F17%2F213454_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=31e4832c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec58fdb9c3bd08fd8c12bc304ad81bcbe22226d","tid":746124,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83f149a566e0113ce5e41a1dc309d7547340ea0a","tid":746124,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95c1afac51a85555b09d2bfe18a3a5e297e21136","tid":746124,"uid":128261,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6a0cfcda3b6a73bed320393416e81ac1de1758c5","tid":746